-Mm-mmm,

01:35.303 --> 01:36.304
Mm-mmm, Mm-mmm,

01:36.387 --> 01:37.847
I have to,

01:37.931 --> 01:41.976
-Ah,
-Or I'll take it as a big insult,

01:46.439 --> 01:47.982
So, so grateful,

01:48.066 --> 01:49.734
-It's nothing,
-Thank you,

01:51.277 --> 01:52.695
Thank you, sir,

01:52.779 --> 01:54.614
