05:31.748 --> 05:34.167
[in English] Look at her,
always acting like a pussycat,

05:34.250 --> 05:36.878
Meanwhile all her teeth
are made of razor blades,

05:36.961 --> 05:38.963
[in Yoruba]
This useless thing,

05:39.630 --> 05:41.549
[in Pidgin] Don't come here
to eat this woman's food,

05:41.632 --> 05:42.717
then start bad-mouthing her,

05:42.800 --> 05:44.177
Her food will choke you,

05:44.260 --> 05:46.512
