31:41.691 --> 31:44.235
[man] Aare is in a meeting
with the party chairman

31:44.319 --> 31:45.904
in the main living room,

31:45.987 --> 31:47.989
He has asked me
to make you feel comfortable

31:48.072 --> 31:49.908
until he is ready to join you,

31:49.991 --> 31:51.993
[TV playing indistinctly]

31:53.286 --> 31:54.662
Please have a seat, ma,

31:54.746 --> 31:56.873
-[Kemi] Thank you,
-Thank you,

32:04.923 --> 32:07.091
[news jingle]

32:07.175 --> 32:09.969
