a glass of cold water?

32:29.155 --> 32:30.323
[man] Yes, ma,

32:30.406 --> 32:32.659
[news anchor] Gobir's appointment
is the latest in efforts

32:32.742 --> 32:35.119
for the organization
to clean up its image, after,,,

