Let's set up, Time is 8:25, No, 8:26 now,

32:40.083 --> 32:41.209
[in Pidgin]
I've set it,

32:41.292 --> 32:44.420
The match will start at 10:01 on the dot,

32:44.504 --> 32:47.256
And the match will end at exactly 11:31,

32:47.340 --> 32:50.843
If Arsenal isn't in the championship
by then, they're on their own, We're out,

32:50.927 --> 32:54.138
We'll be there,
Don't worry, we'll be there,

32:59.852 --> 33:01.813
[news anchor]
Gobir's disgraced predecessor,,,

33:01.896 --> 33:03.398
[man] Eniola!

33:03.481 --> 33:06.609
[chuckles]
Eniola! Good girl,

33:06.693 --> 33:09.362
-Good evening, sir,
-How are you?

33:09.445 --> 33:11.656
Ah! Who is this? Ah!

33:12.365 --> 33:16.953
Is this not Adekemi of yesterday?
That used to look like a boy,

33:17.036 --> 33:19.956
-[chuckles]
-Ah, the work of God,

33:20.039 --> 33:22.458
you cannot find it
even if you look for it,

33:22.542 --> 33:25.420
Look at how God
has put everything one by one

33:25.503 --> 33:29.590
in every place
and everything is perfection, Ah!

33:29.674 --> 33:31.342
[in Yoruba]
She is our daughter,

33:31.426 --> 33:33.261
Stand up,
Stand up and sit down,

33:33.344 --> 33:36.931
-Thank you, sir,
-Ah, ah, Welcome, Sorry,

33:37.015 --> 33:38.725
[news anchor] The Nigerian government

33:38.808 --> 33:41.019
has officially signed
its whistle-blower policy

33:41.102 --> 33:42.937
which encourages citizens

33:43.021 --> 33:46.232
to report suspected financial crimes
to the authorities,

33:46.816 --> 33:48.860
The policy put in place

33:48.943 --> 33:53.072
in conjunction with the Attorney General,
the federation and the Ministry of Justice

33:53.156 --> 33:57.243
offers five percent of all moneys
recovered to whistle-blowers,

33:57.326 --> 33:59.162
irrespective of amount,

33:59.746 --> 34:03.916
Imagine the rubbish, Huh?
Imagine this rubbish,

34:04.834 --> 34:09.755
They are encouraging criminals
to harass us

34:09.839 --> 34:12.382
and to blackmail us,

34:12.467 --> 34:16.763
Huh? Is this the reason
why we put him there?

34:16.846 --> 34:19.724
Why we appointed him as president? Huh?

34:19.806 --> 34:22.935
It's the "Corruption today,
corruption tomorrow,

34:23.018 --> 34:25.521
corruption, corruption everywhere!"

34:25.605 --> 34:27.982
Is that what we are going to be eating?

34:28.065 --> 34:30.318
